title: I can't download Oce legends
body:
I have been trying to download league and update it since 6.3 came out and i can't launch oceanic league but another region works out fine but i live in oceanic and my account is on oce too

Pls help if you have any suggestions

replies.body:
Hey there,

Could you please try [switching to a public DNS](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues#wq5) and let me know if that helps.
i tried but however it didn't work, changing my DNS
Do you receive an error when attempting to switch to OCE through the launcher?
when i change to oceanic an error pops up saying "update failed unspecified error pls check logs for more information"

Could you reply with a link to your patcher logs?

These can be found in the following path

>C:\Riot Games\League of Legends\Logs\Patcher Logs

Preferably only upload the few most recent log files.
How do u want me to upload them to u
Feel free to upload them to the wrenchmen upload site, [here](http://upload.wrenchmen.org/)
is there any other way thats possible?

There's plenty of free services that will host your content, [Mega](http://mega.co.nz/) is one that is decently good.

What's wrong with the wrenchmen upload service?
lets say i dont know how to upload it because i'm using a mac currently and im not very familiar with it

Oh, if you mentioned you were on a Mac earlier I could've provided more direct help.

[Here](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues#mq4) is a guide on how to switch to a public DNS on Mac.

Your logs can be found in the following directory

>Applications/League of Legends/Logs/Patcher Logs

Have you followed the steps above to switch to a public DNS?

Could I also get you to run the following command in your terminal (after you've switched to a public DNS as linked in previous posts), If you don't know how to open your terminal I've included an image below. (Click on it to display the full image)

http://i.imgur.com/10nFokA.png

>sudo dscacheutil -flushcache;sudo killall -HUP mDNSResponder; say cache flushed

After you've done this, reboot the machine and let me know if the issue persists.
Could you please provide the latest log file for me to look at.
i tried changing my dns and entering the command into my terminal and still the same message pops up when i open my LoL launcher

Hey Cycl0p3s, 

I'll try to help where I can! Can you try the solutions in the Troubleshooting Patching Issues thread linked below?

http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-oce/PuEpZLzo-having-patching-issues-try-these-solutions
this is very frustrating to me because any other region i can download, all except Oceanic :(
